<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>7940</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15111</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在美丽的夏威夷岛上，一个有权威的酋长与他的女儿一起生活着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15114</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17582</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她是热带地区的公主。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17583</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21189</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们在岛上生活得很幸福。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21190</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27954</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一天，公主因为吃了变质的芒果，觉得很难受。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27955</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30604</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>酋长叫来了巫医。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30605</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40913</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巫医摇摇头难过地说，“只有一个办法能救您的女儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40914</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44392</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>您必须找到三朵金花。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44393</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50322</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它们长在阳光照射的闪闪发光的水里。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50323</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57778</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>酋长想让他的女儿活下来，所以他召集了村庄里所有的男人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57779</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63802</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他告诉他们谁能拿到三朵金花，就可以娶公主。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63803</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68777</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>住在河对面的三个兄弟听到了这个消息。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68778</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75586</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们只是贫穷的农民，但是他们很了解这天堂般的小岛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75587</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81357</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>只有这三兄弟知道那能治病的神秘之花在哪里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81358</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86610</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第一个兄弟坐上小船向上游划去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86611</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91530</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他在一个金光闪闪的瀑布旁找到了金花。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91531</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98125</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他知道在那个特别的地方一年只生长出九朵花。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98126</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101909</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他摘下了那三朵神奇的花。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101910</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>正当他划船要回到村庄的时候，一位年老的渔夫把他拦了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109536</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113266</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那是什么？”渔夫问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113267</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118977</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>男孩儿不相信这个老人，于是回答，“是蠕虫。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118978</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124298</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>男孩儿到达村庄后把篮子拿给酋长看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124299</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130527</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是打开篮子后只看到了蠕虫，而没有三朵金花。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130528</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135365</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天，第二个兄弟也遇到了同样的事情。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135366</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138893</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>酋长很伤心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138894</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143254</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>于是第三个兄弟决定去试一试。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143255</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148104</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他最年轻，而且天性善良，还很害羞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148105</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153710</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当渔夫问他篮子里装的是什么的时候，他很诚实。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153711</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158082</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他说，“我有三朵金花。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158083</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163223</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>渔夫向篮子里看了一下，“确实有。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163224</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167238</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你可能会需要这根长笛。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167239</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173584</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>神奇的花治好了公主的病，但是酋长却不守信用。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178580</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他不想让一个贫穷的农民娶他的女儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178581</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183969</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>酋长说，“今晚把这一百只鸟带出去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183970</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192342</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果你明天早上能把这些鸟都带回来，你就可以娶我的女儿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192343</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200248</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是在月光之下，那个可怜的男孩儿很快就把所有的鸟都弄丢了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200249</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204498</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>于是他想到了渔夫送给他的长笛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204499</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他开始吹奏那神奇的长笛，所有的鸟都飞回来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213977</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>酋长非常惊讶！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213978</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219587</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>难道这个贫穷的男孩儿给那一百只鸟都施了魔法？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219588</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222420</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把鸟数了两次。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222421</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230380</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后酋长郑重地向男孩儿低下了头说，“你有资格娶我女儿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230381</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235799</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个贫穷的男孩儿让全家人都住到了酋长的村庄。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235800</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240615</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在这里他和他的妻子幸福地生活着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240616</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247503</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>偶尔，早春时节，阳光照射在瀑布上熠熠生辉，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247512</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256680</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个年轻的男人和他的妻子会坐在瀑布旁看着金色的花朵。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>